param.string: CASE WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 1, 3) IN ('R01', 'R03', 'R05', 'R12') THEN 'income' ELSE CASE WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 1, 3) IN ('R02', 'R06', 'R16', 'R13', 'R14', 'R15') THEN 'expense' ELSE 'na' END END

CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica LIKE 'R0108%' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica LIKE 'R0109%' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica LIKE 'R0208%' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica LIKE 'R0808%' THEN 'na' ELSE 'amortisedCost' END

CASE WHEN (($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica LIKE 'R01%' AND $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica NOT LIKE 'R0109%') OR ($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica LIKE 'R0109%' AND $Aggregation.mvyt24be_gl_account LIKE '5052%') OR ($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica LIKE 'R0210%' AND $Aggregation.mvyt24be_gl_account LIKE '4042%') OR ($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica LIKE 'R0802%' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica LIKE 'R0803%' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica LIKE 'R0804%')) THEN 'asset' ELSE CASE WHEN (($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica LIKE 'R02%' AND $Aggregation.mvyt24be_gl_account NOT LIKE '4042%') OR ($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica LIKE 'R0806%')) THEN 'liability' ELSE 'na' END END

CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica IN ('A04020501','A04040501','A05030201','A05030301','A050401','A050601') THEN 'yes' 	WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 0, 5) = 'P0802' THEN 'yes' 	WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica, 0, 5) = 'P0804' THEN 'yes' 	ELSE 'no' END
CASE  WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica like 'A06%' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica like 'O0501%' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica like 'O0502%' THEN 'yes' ELSE 'no' END

CASE  	 	WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_morosity = 'STA' THEN 'no' 	 	WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_morosity = 'WAT' THEN 'no' 	 	WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_morosity IN ('DBT','SUB','WRI') THEN 'yes' 	ELSE 'na' END
CASE WHEN ($Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica LIKE 'A%' OR $Aggregation.mvyt24be_rubrica LIKE 'R%') AND $Notice_Period.GL_Null_Notice_Period IS NULL THEN 99999 ELSE NULL END

CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_product_group IN ('DEPOSITS', 'DEPOSITS.FLEXIBLE', 'DEMAND.ACCOUNTS', 'SAVING.ACCOUNTS', 'SAVING.HOUSING', 'LOANS', 'COLLECTIONS')   AND $Aggregation.mvyt24be_end_date IS NULL THEN 'sight'  	 WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_product_group IN ('DEPOSITS', 'DEPOSITS.FLEXIBLE', 'DEMAND.ACCOUNTS', 'SAVING.ACCOUNTS', 'SAVING.HOUSING', 'LOANS', 'COLLECTIONS')   AND $Aggregation.mvyt24be_end_date IS NOT NULL THEN 'term'   ELSE 'na' END

CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_risk_type = 'ST1' THEN 'stage1' ELSE CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_risk_type = 'ST2' THEN 'stage2' ELSE CASE WHEN $Aggregation.mvyt24be_risk_type = 'ST3' THEN 'stage3' END END END
CASE WHEN @subStr($Aggregation.mvyt24be_gl_account, 0, 6) IN ('26403','26404') THEN 'yes' ELSE 'no' END
